# Deploy after changes

After implementing any requested changes to this project:

1. Run `git add` for the modified (and any new) files.
2. Run `git commit` with a clear, short message describing the change.
3. Run `git push` to push to origin (e.g. ayna_mvp1 on GitHub).

The user relies on Vercel to preview the site; pushing to the connected branch triggers a new deploy.
